# ── Paid LimeZu pixel tiles — license forbids redistribution ──
# The canvas-2D "living world" front-end (public/phase-two/*.html) IS tracked on
# this branch, but its tile library is extracted from Riley's paid LimeZu purchase
# and must never reach a public remote. Tiles live on disk only; to repopulate a
# fresh clone, re-extract from ~/Documents/Repositories/godot-sanctuary/
# {modernexteriors-win,moderninteriors-win}. See memory: living-world-art-target.
public/phase-two/lz/
